      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 14:51:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Natwest 是泰晤士水务债务传奇核心的贷款代理</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/natwest-is-agent-on-loan-at-heart-of-thames-water-debt-saga</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据两位知情人士透露，Natwest Group Plc 是泰晤士水务母公司一笔 1.9 亿英镑（合 2.39 亿美元）贷款的代理人，这笔贷款将于本月晚些时候偿还。由于细节保密，他们要求不具名。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/natwest-is-agent-on-loan-at-heart-of-thames-water-debt-saga</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 14:43:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美联储鲍曼希望密切关注银行贴现窗口的使用</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/fed-s-bowman-flags-discount-window-use-as-area-of-concern</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储理事米歇尔·鲍曼表示，央行应权衡在审查贷方流动性资源时是否应承认贴现窗口借款能力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/fed-s-bowman-flags-discount-window-use-as-area-of-concern</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 13:38:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>越南总理敦促“大力”推动 GDP 增长 6.5%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/vietnam-s-pm-urges-drastic-push-to-reach-2024-6-5-gdp-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据政府网站上的一份声明，越南总理范明正敦促各部委和省级政府采取“严厉行动”，使国家能够实现今年 6.5% 的增长目标。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-03/vietnam-s-pm-urges-drastic-push-to-reach-2024-6-5-gdp-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Apr 2024 07:11:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
